---
import Section from './ui/Section.astro';
// Actualizado para Acratos
---

<Section 
  id="welcome"
  hideDecoration
  className="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-24">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
        <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-purple-400 to-teal-400">
          La Próxima Era de Internet es Tuya
        </span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Acratos está construyendo una red descentralizada que devuelve el control a los usuarios.
        Sin intermediarios, sin censura, sin límites.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a 
          href="#why-acratos" 
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-purple-700 text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/30"
        >
          Descubre cómo
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#whitepaper" 
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-gray-800/50 hover:bg-gray-700/50 border border-gray-700/50 hover:border-indigo-500/30 text-white font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Lee el Whitepaper
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  /* Efecto de partículas en el fondo */
  #welcome {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  #welcome::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) 0%, transparent 20%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1) 0%, transparent 20%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 80%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, transparent 20%);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  #links a.button {
    color: white;
    background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12),
      inset 0 -2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  #links a.button:hover {
    color: rgb(230, 230, 230);
    box-shadow: none;
  }
